17 | /**
18 |  * The hero comparison: vanilla on the left, AutorIA in-voice on the right.
19 |  * Both branches come from the same POST /generate call, so their states
20 |  * usually move together — but each column owns its own state so a single
21 |  * branch can fail or lag without hiding the other.
